    <title><![CDATA[ASP.NET的MD5加密方式]]></title>
    <link href="http://blog.wabzsy.com/2012/08/22/ASP-NET%E7%9A%84MD5%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F/"/>
    <id>http://blog.wabzsy.com/2012/08/22/ASP-NET的MD5加密方式/</id>
    <published>2012-08-22T08:00:27.000Z</published>
    <updated>2014-10-05T17:36:33.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>添加命名空间:</p>
<figure class="highlight {csharp}"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> System.Security.Cryptography;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> System.<span class="built_in">Text</span>;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>自己写了个方法:</p>
<figure class="highlight {csharp}"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> Safe</div><div class="line">{</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">string</span> <span class="title">Md5</span>(<span class="keyword">string</span> str)</div><div class="line">    {</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">try</span></div><div class="line">        {</div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">byte</span>[] hashvalue = (<span class="keyword">new</span> MD5CryptoServiceProvider()).ComputeHash(Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str));</div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> BitConverter.ToString(hashvalue);</div><div class="line">        }</div><div class="line">        <span class="keyword">catch</span></div><div class="line">        {</div><div class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> String.Empty;</div><div class="line">        }</div><div class="line">    }</div><div class="line">}</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>然后调用时使用:</p>
<figure class="highlight {csharp}"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="attribute">string password </span>=<span class="string"> Safe.Md5(&quot;Your Password&quot;);</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>就可以实现Md5加密了..</p>
<p>ASP.NET(C#)的md5比较特殊,是47位:00-11-22-33-44-55-66-77-88-99-AA-BB-CC-DD-EE-FF这种形式的,</p>
<p>所以在数据库里添加字段时不要建成常规的32位,要不然会出现&#8221;将截断字符串或二进制数据&#8221;这种错误.</p>
]]></content>
